---
import { SITE } from "../config";
---

<section id="about" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-[clamp(4rem,10vh,8rem)]">
  <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-[1fr_280px] md:gap-16">
    <div class="max-w-[65ch]">
      <h2 class="display reveal text-[clamp(1.9rem,5vw,3.2rem)]">
        About this <span class="text-[var(--color-aurora)]">portfolio</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="reveal-blur mt-8 space-y-5 leading-[1.75] text-[var(--color-body)]" style="--d:120ms">
        <p>
          Welcome to the official <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">{SITE.name} website</strong>,
          a developer portfolio built to showcase real, production-grade work. I'm
          <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">{SITE.name}</strong>, a {SITE.role.toLowerCase()} based
          in {SITE.location} with 2+ years of experience designing, building and deploying scalable web
          applications. This portfolio website is the best place to understand how I think, what I ship,
          and how I can help turn an idea into a fast, reliable product.
        </p>

        <p>
          As a <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">full stack developer</strong>, I work across the
          entire stack: crafting responsive front ends with React, Next.js and modern CSS, and building
          secure back ends with Python, Django and the Django REST Framework. At Sanadi Technologies I
          designed and shipped a modular ERP platform end-to-end, with multiple departments, RESTful APIs and
          a clean React interface, used in real day-to-day business operations.
        </p>

        <p>
          What sets this developer portfolio apart is the cloud and DevOps depth behind it. I provision
          and run complete <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">AWS</strong> infrastructure (EC2, S3,
          RDS, VPC, IAM, Lambda and API Gateway), containerise applications with
          <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">Docker</strong>, orchestrate them on
          <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">Kubernetes</strong> for 99.9% uptime, and automate
          provisioning with Ansible. I'm a Red Hat Certified Engineer (RHCE) and CISCO CCNA, with a strong
          Linux, networking and Bash scripting background, so the apps I build don't just look good: they
          deploy and scale reliably.
        </p>

        <p>
          I also love building <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">AI-powered web applications</strong>.
          You can explore that work in the projects section below: EduFlow, an AI learning management
          system powered by Llama 3.3 that gives every student a 24/7 tutor; ResumeAI, a tool that tailors
          résumés to boost interview rates and automates job applications; a conversion-focused marketing
          site for an events business; and a task manager with authentication. Every project on this
          portfolio is live, so you can click through and try it yourself instead of just reading about it.
        </p>

        <p>
          I believe a portfolio should do more than look good. It should rank, load instantly and earn
          trust. That's why this website is statically generated with Astro for near-instant performance,
          ships semantic HTML and structured data so search engines understand exactly who I am, and
          includes proper Open Graph and Twitter meta tags so every shared link looks sharp. If you
          searched for a <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">developer portfolio</strong>, a
          <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">full stack developer portfolio</strong>, or for the
          <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">{SITE.name} portfolio</strong>, you're in the right place.
        </p>

        <p>
          Whether you're a recruiter evaluating candidates, a founder who needs an MVP shipped quickly, or
          a team that wants a fast, modern website that actually ranks on Google, I'd love to talk. I take
          pride in writing maintainable code, communicating clearly and delivering on time. Browse my
          experience, skills and projects below, and when something resonates, reach out through the
          contact section. Thanks for visiting my portfolio website; let's build something worth shipping.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="reveal md:pt-24" style="--d:200ms">
      <div class="relative mx-auto w-56 md:w-full">
        <div class="absolute -inset-3 rounded-3xl bg-[oklch(0.55_0.12_162/0.25)] blur-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <img
          src={SITE.photo}
          alt={`${SITE.name}, ${SITE.role} in Bangalore`}
          width="340"
          height="340"
          loading="lazy"
          class="relative aspect-square w-full rounded-3xl border border-[oklch(0.8_0.165_162/0.35)] object-cover"
        />
        <div class="hud mt-4 space-y-1.5 text-center md:text-left">
          <p>RHCE · EX294 // CISCO CCNA</p>
          <p>M.TECH RVCE · BANGALORE</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
